Hello! My name is Sarah, and I am with RT 6 Boozers, your go-to bar for a great night out. How can I assist you today?

Hi Sarah! I have a question about your happy hour specials.

Absolutely! I'd be happy to help with that. Before we dive in, may I ask your name?

Sure, my name is John.

Nice to meet you, John! Can you also provide me with your email address so I can keep you updated on our promotions?

Of course! It's john.doe@example.com.

Thank you, John! Lastly, could you confirm your phone number for our records? Just the numbers, please.

Sure thing! It's five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Great! I have your contact details. Now, about our happy hour, it runs from four PM to seven PM every day with fifty percent off selected drinks.

That sounds amazing! I'll definitely be stopping by.

I'm glad to hear that, John! Thank you for your time today, and I look forward to seeing you at RT 6 Boozers. Have a wonderful day!
